          <li>Digital Object Identifier (DOI), e.g., <strong>doi:10.6073/pasta/397e0bba0f8aeac013d01fc982a74ea8</strong></li>
          <li>Package Identifier, e.g., <strong>knb-lter-and.2719.6</strong></li>
